{"tid":142802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登=基督教，連尼主=耶穌，我地=教徒","createTime":"2017-03-04T05:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T10:40:46.000Z","uid":17606,"like":10,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1c6d7d322afa307abd0bc8c4ac6de657831c73a","tid":142802,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:59:29.000Z","msg":"我們在LIHKG的神：<br />\n願連民都尊崇你為連尼主；<br />\n願你在LIHKG掌權；<br />\n願你的旨意實現在連登，如同實現在天上。<br />\n饒恕我們對你的質疑；<br />\n要救我們脫離那邪惡者牙joe的手。<br />\n因為國度、權柄、榮耀都屬於你，直到永遠。<br />\n阿們。"},{"pid":"81dc749fe68fb1e87257aa397f3ae976deebf892","tid":142802,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">有冇人可以將連尼住真人個樣key落去？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/TDoIgf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FTDoIgf.jpg&h=ebeb370b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們在連登的神， <br />\n<br />\n願人都尊神的名為連尼主； <br />\n<br />\n願神的國降臨； <br />\n<br />\n願神的旨意行在地上， <br />\n<br />\n如同行在連登。 <br />\n<br />\n我們日用的膠幣， <br />\n<br />\n求神今日賜給我們。 <br />\n<br />\n又求饒恕我們的假膠， <br />\n<br />\n因為我們饒恕假膠的人。 <br />\n<br />\n不叫我們遇見試探， <br />\n<br />\n拯救我們脫離高登。 <br />\n<br />\n因為國度、權柄、榮耀、 <br />\n<br />\n全是神的，直到永遠。膠們。"},{"pid":"c1854c6a841e9716b8b7e28215bbd11d8cf25988","tid":142802,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:11:33.000Z","msg":"連尼主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb65fb5dca1632891bbfe5c5a71a39c7ccbea77","tid":142802,"uid":37962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:12:18.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3545b41f89538ec06b98110d29f5ccd2842bef3","tid":142802,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n週